title: Fendi Selleria Baguette Shoulder Bag
description: Fendi medium Selleria Baguette shoulder bag in brown calfskin leather. Featuring silver-toned hardware, tone-to-tone Selleria stitching, and FF square logo plate on front flap. The magnetic button opens to a light brown microfiber interior with a zip pocket. Approximate dimensions: 27.5cm(L) x 15cm(H) x 6cm(D), detachable and adjustable handle drop 14cm. Accompanied by a Fendi dustbag. With Entrupy Certificate of Authenticity. (Pre-owned)
